Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這麼痛苦的回憶的話 我將不再向他人渴求甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十六歲的冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.97,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體驗了能撕裂身心的痛苦離別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.48,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}白色花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到聖誕節了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的初次相遇是在春天的某一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早晨 我比平常早了很多地來到了學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中二年級的我對甚麼都感到厭煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是這個宛如天使牧場的學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是帶著純真微笑的學生們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界一定是正確的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.29,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就是無法適應它的壞羔羊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救這樣的我吧 阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼非得和大家一起笑不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼非得去聽那些毫無興趣的話題不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我保持著沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連做甚麼好或是想去做甚麼也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也別碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的事情全部忘掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的內心中沒有一絲的滋潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一個人困在一片乾涸的荒野中無路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.32,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著大人樣的她 看起來全身充滿著我所沒有的滋潤的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還是第一次聽到\n從你嘴裡冒出別人的名字來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.27,0:03:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是今早認識了一個那樣的一年級生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的內心中 有甚麼東西正在開始變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.23,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.32,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖 你作為花蕾的自覺好像太少了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 有稀客在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.13,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為祥子長得跟日本娃娃一樣漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不由自主地就想招待她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我長得一副洋味十足的臉孔真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 鬧彆扭了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我喜歡聖的臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是憑臉孔選的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為我想一直看著這張臉 所以請待在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.31,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這一句話 我決定成為她的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡這樣單純而明快的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.52,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 從一開始姐姐對待我的方式就非常地高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變得連自已都吃驚的積極起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼事嗎？ 聖大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學今天休假了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概在聖堂那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像理所當然似的{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}出現在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.18,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為被這個世界所愛的潔白而閃耀的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 白薔薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心情...會讓你為難嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將自已完全地暴露 追尋著依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全不再有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直想著要見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.06,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於在這個學園裡能遇見{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想從心裡對神說聲感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在可利用的時間裡我們都儘量單獨相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越遠離薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷陷入了{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微保持一點距離不是更好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果想認妹妹 那到也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式地交與念珠 好好地向大家介紹一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我可以走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有打算認{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.79,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹的儀式\n是那些沒有像徵就無法安心的人們做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從心底嘲笑著這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.06,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 我們雙方各自都將\n與生俱來的雙手連結到了同一個人的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個結果就是將其它的東西完全地排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被說了甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了嗎？ 游泳的補習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.36,0:07:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事故中喪失了雙親的{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}一直住在學生宿舍裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}沒有回到長崎的叔叔那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是留在了東京的某個修道院裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時在這裡避避雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.01,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒甚麼關係 擦擦你自已的頭髮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼我們 會作為不同的個體出生到這個世上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼 你再睡一會兒也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了後我會叫醒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨啊 別停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間就這樣停止好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想與{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}溶為一體然後消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種心情究竟是甚麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向自已以外的人渴求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路的前方又是哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.75,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個答案恐怕永遠也找不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最真實的東西只有{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的悸動 體溫和吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這些就是我所期望的這個世界的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的心中{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的存在膨脹得越來越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在薔薇館的時間變得越來越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也想和你一起喝喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.38,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷絕與我的姐妹之緣 重新找一個妹妹如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要違反約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.45,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我畢業以前 你可要好好地待在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.05,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不認妹妹 那也沒甚麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走你自已不會後悔的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擺出那副表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像我是瘟神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是說教嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明對我們的事甚麼也不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你又知道{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「甚麼」是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是不要陷得太深為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要特意來說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想看到你受傷的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果不在了你會怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}會...不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚麼都沒聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學畢業後會進入修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要成為修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進入這間學校之前就已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要隱瞞到現在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒有機會說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了也不會有甚麼改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然很喜歡{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻不喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個畢業前的陪伴… 你是這樣隨便地考慮的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會這麼喜歡一個人也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為甚麼要成為修女甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 你寧願選擇神嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是只有{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拋棄我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要像那樣逼問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為修女是我的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為甚麼不敢看著我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在迷惑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖母瑪莉亞在看著我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸給了聖母瑪莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的上課態度變得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結業式的那天 我受到傳喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她已經再沒有甚麼關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}也是這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是自已的錯之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}也被叫來這裡了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一頭陷入一樣東西中而看不清周圍 不是一件很寂寞的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.63,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}兩日前提出了外宿申請 無論在宿舍還是修道院都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 怎樣才能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在薔薇館會開一個聯歡會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令會為大家做好吃的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有心情的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 好想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.04,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在見不著你的時候 我只是想著你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使做祈禱 也沒法讓你的樣子離開腦海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.57,0:15:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長非常擔心我們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做過約定不再見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r} 一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.13,0:15:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未知的土地上 不被任何人打擾的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.96,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和聖在一起 到哪裡都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好行李就過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在車站等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}微笑著目送我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忘記那個微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定的時間已過去3小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}已經不會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我仍無法離開月台的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.30,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法捨棄也許{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}\n馬上就會從那個樓梯下來的僅有的一點希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是做夢 我也想見到{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.15,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學來接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學好像不會與你一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.33,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}同學好像曾經來過這個車站一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠處注視著在月台上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後覺得果然還是不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然來了為甚麼不直接...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見面後會讓決心變弱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變弱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她看起來很有大人樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟仍只是高中一年級生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會動搖也是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}會去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聽說會轉學到很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是她接受了的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有遇見我的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠相遇是件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能創造可以坦然回想著\n「能夠相遇真好」的未來 那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種未來一定無法來臨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕總有一天會瘉合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你不是還有我在身邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.03,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是真以為我只愛著你的臉孔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮 那只是為了不增加你負擔的一個方便的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對待你的方式可是很高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐不是就要畢業了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會擔心你的可不只是我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是令做的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經向聖的母親打了電話說你要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.18,0:19:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始就是開心的寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就玩到深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安安靜靜地鬧它一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期已經變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.02,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕前夜過去 我知道自己已是十七歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 {\fs41\fnsimhei}栞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日誠子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 也就是須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去大波斯菊編緝部時 曾見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉前段時間失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.52,0:20:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的學生給您添了不少麻煩真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是佐藤 聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 今天是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來見學園長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那麼 我來為您帶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我知道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過去一點也沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安的畢業生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 據說已知道香織還活著的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要在聖誕前夜去見香織的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是說香織在這裡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 去見學園長是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 是這樣啊 學園長就是香織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兩個人在隔了這麼多年後終於可以再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.71,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯歡會要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.74,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.05,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Happy Birthday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從波折的姐妹宣言開始 終於到了現在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.10,0:23:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就是初次的約會 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.01,0:23:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不認為和你的約會能夠平安無事就結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後也不會讓你厭煩的 姐姐
